<paragraph base="F31460630" principles="yes" id="IFRS15_1"><paranum>1</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 15"/><data name="paranum" value="1"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS15_P0013">The objective of this Standard is to establish the principles that an entity shall apply to report useful information to users of financial statements about the nature, amount, timing and uncertainty of <xref base="F31716757" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_DI0007" scope="local"><i>revenue</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0341"/></ph></xref> and cash flows arising from a <xref base="F31716726" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_DI0001" scope="local"><i>contract</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0049"/></ph></xref> with a <xref base="F31716738" href="IFRS15_APPA.dita#IFRS15_APPA/IFRS15_DI0004" scope="local"><i>customer</i><ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_customer"/></ph></xref>.</p></body></paragraph>